text: Piyathip Sansaniyakulvilai (born 23 October 1972) is a Thai badminton player. She competed in women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Thai female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Thailand Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics
